    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Project Arrhythmia&quot; is a musical bullet-hell in which all things beautiful are deadly. A cacophony of lights, music, pulses and blocks, Project Arrhythmia features tight bullet-hell style gameplay where up to 4 players in local co-op must navigate their way through evolving scenes and obstacles, all timed to the beat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in 207X, a mysterious disease called &quot;LNNS&quot; has been ravaging the world. A lone AI researcher, Anna Schroeder, attempts to find the cure with her trusty supercomputer companion HAL. Stumbling upon various “Projects,” the duo decides to investigate the efficacy of a cure using a pulse/rhythm-based interface. <strong><i>Work in progress.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CURRENT FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dodge The Beat:</strong> Stages consist of mesmerizing, musically timed scenes, each one telling a story. Feel the rhythm and feel your way around the hazards! Anna will judge how you do.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Your Friends:</strong> Up to 4 players supported in local co-op mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robust Level Editor:</strong> A carefully designed level editor allows users to create their own levels and challenges using whatever music they wish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Huge Community:</strong> A Wealth of user-created content exists, fully integrated into the game through the usage of the level editor and user-made levels. Already, 2000+ community levels have been uploaded, and more are being made daily.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode Demo:</strong> Currently, the game features a short 5+ story levels as a demo for the upcoming complete story mode. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPCOMING FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete Story Mode:</strong> Over 20+ hand-crafted heart-pounding levels interwoven with an engaging story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant Updates:</strong> More features come with bi-weekly updates to keep the game fresh.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Some screenshots used are from UGC:</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sleep Cannon by cozm</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Excelsus by DXL44</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Lucid by Taikeb0</i></p></li></ul>",
